{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"text":" in its ","type":